<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 8. Head (lateral) I a O. ahoma (Mani & Kaul) (imaged specimen: OAh 01, holotype) b O. circularicollis sp. n. (OCi 01, holotype) c O. felix sp. n. (OFe 01, holotype) d O. fidelis sp. n. (OFi 01, holotype) e O. florea sp. n. (OFl 01, holotype) f O. formosa (Giraud) (OFo 06). Scale bars: 1 mm." , "Figure 11. Mesosoma (dorsal) I a O. ahoma (Mani & Kaul) (imaged specimen: OAh 01, holotype) b O. circularicollis sp. n. (OCi 01, holotype), c O. felix sp. n. (OFe 01, holotype) d O. fidelis sp. n. (OFi 01, holotype) e O. florea sp. n. (OFl 01, holotype) f O. formosa (Giraud) (OFo 03). Scale bars: 1 mm." , "Figure 14. Mesoscutellum and propodeum (dorsal) I a O. ahoma (Mani & Kaul) (imaged specimen: OAh 01, holotype) b O. circularicollis sp. n. (OCi 01, holotype) c O. felix sp. n. (OFe 01, holotype) d O. fidelis sp. n. (OFi 01, holotype) e O. florea sp. n. (OFl 01, holotype), f O. formosa (Giraud) (OFo 14). Scale bars: 1 mm." , "Figure 4. Habitus (dorsal) III a O. magnifica (Risbec) (imaged specimen: OMag 01, holotype) b O. mkomaziensis sp. n. (OMk 01, holotype) c O. monstrum syn. n. (OFo 12, paratype) d O. namibiensis sp. n. (ONa 01, holotype) e O. niehuisorum sp. n. (ONi 01, holotype) f O. pumilae Yang (OPu 01, paratype) g O. regiae Yang (ORe 01, paratype) h O. srilankiensis sp. n. (OSr 01, holotype) i O. tenuicollis (Walker) (OTe 01, holotype). Scale bars: 1 mm." , "Figure 2. Habitus (dorsal) I a O. ahoma (Mani & Kaul) (imaged specimen: OAh 01, holotype) b O. circularicollis sp. n. (OCi 01, holotype), c O. felix sp. n. (OFe 01, holotype) d O. fidelis sp. n. (OFi 01, holotype) e O. florea sp. n. (OFl 01, holotype) f O. formosa (Giraud) (OFo 13). Scale bars: 1 mm." , "Figure 5. Head (frontal) I a O. ahoma (Mani & Kaul) (imaged specimen: OAh 01, holotype) b O. circularicollis sp. n. (OCi 01, holotype) c O. felix sp. n. (OFe 01, holotype) d O. fidelis sp. n. (OFi 01, holotype) e O. florea sp. n. (OFl 01, holotype) f O. formosa (Giraud) (OFo 03). Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/199725" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/199732" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/199726" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/199735" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/199729" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/199723" .

